  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To explore how a clinical sample of patients with thyroid nodules (men and women) with no
      history of thyroid cancer would make decisions about treatments based on different
      terminology used to describe papillary thyroid cancer (with and without the cancer term).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
